  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育系统的服务依赖关系建一个看板。核心是看板分成三列，分别对应ClassroomService、StudentDB和GradeSync这三个关键服务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1",
        "column2",
        "column3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。第一列叫Education_ClassroomService，第二列Education_StudentDB，第三列Education_GradeSync。每列里放依赖该服务的上游组件，这样理解对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1",
        "column2",
        "column3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个逻辑。比如ClassroomService这一列，里面要放依赖它的服务。StudentDB和ClassroomService本身都依赖它，所以作为任务卡片放进去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1",
        "task1",
        "task2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在第一列Education_ClassroomService里添加了两个任务：Education_StudentDB和Education_ClassroomService本身。第二列StudentDB目前空着，等您确认放什么。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1",
        "task1",
        "task2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第二列StudentDB里放一个ClassroomService，因为实际部署中ClassroomService也反向依赖StudentDB的数据同步。第三列GradeSync要放LMS_Portal，这是成绩同步的入口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column2",
        "column3",
        "task3",
        "task4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：第二列Education_StudentDB放入Education_ClassroomService任务，第三列Education_GradeSync放入Education_LMS_Portal任务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column2",
        "column3",
        "task3",
        "task4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我检查一下。第一列里的第二个任务，名称应该是ClassroomService，但前面我让你写的是Education_ClassroomService，这个命名会不会和列名重复造成混淆？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "task2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确实，task2目前显示为Education_ClassroomService，和列名Education_ClassroomService完全一致。这在看板里会让人觉得是同一层级。需要调整吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1",
        "task2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不用改，这个重复是故意的。它表示ClassroomService服务在自我依赖的语境下——比如服务启动时要检查自身健康状态。保持原样，这是正确的业务含义。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "task2"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了，保留Education_ClassroomService作为任务卡片。那整体结构现在是这样：三列服务，每列包含1-2个依赖该服务的组件。需要我再核对一遍所有元素吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1",
        "column2",
        "column3",
        "task1",
        "task2",
        "task3",
        "task4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "核对一下：第一列ClassroomService下有StudentDB和ClassroomService；第二列StudentDB下有ClassroomService；第三列GradeSync下有LMS_Portal。这个依赖方向对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1",
        "column2",
        "column3",
        "task1",
        "task2",
        "task3",
        "task4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认无误。不过有个细节想确认：task3是ClassroomService放在StudentDB列下，表示ClassroomService依赖StudentDB；而task1是StudentDB放在ClassroomService列下，表示StudentDB依赖ClassroomService。这是双向依赖的设计吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "task1",
        "task3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，实际系统中确实存在循环依赖。ClassroomService需要StudentDB存取学生数据，StudentDB也需要ClassroomService的上下文来完成权限校验。双向依赖是符合真实架构的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "task1",
        "task3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的。那第三列的LMS_Portal作为GradeSync的依赖方，是成绩数据推送到门户的流向对吧？这个没有反向依赖？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column3",
        "task4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，LMS_Portal是纯消费方，单向接收GradeSync的成绩数据。这个看板现在完整了，三列四个任务卡片，覆盖了我们核心的服务依赖拓扑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column3",
        "task4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "最终看板已确认：Education_ClassroomService列含StudentDB与ClassroomService；Education_StudentDB列含ClassroomService；Education_GradeSync列含LMS_Portal。结构完整，可以定稿。",
      "elements_involved": [
